    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that\u2019s been really well-cared for? I'm selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in such great shape! It runs like a dream and has been perfect for getting around town. It's super clean, dependable, and ready to hit the road with a new owner. I\u2019ve loved driving this beauty, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
