    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six benefits from recent VANOS servicing and subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with the factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the communicative steering feel these units are known for. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the powertrain maintains excellent compression and thermal efficiency. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
